<Class name="CM_VehicleBookingTimeSlot" id="21a42323-a4f0-4194-9ab7-c58c67356f6e">
    <superclass name="CM_VehicleBookings"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>

		Represents a booking for a carrier /  Truck  /  Driver to turn up at the gate.
		Booking hasn't been used if the vehicle visit record is empty, otherwise links to the truck that used it.
		
		Terminal config determines if driver and truck mandatory, other wise can be just against the carrier.</text>
